{"word":"Heathen","slug":"heathen","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Heathen</b> All who are not embraced under the Abrahamic covenant.<br/> Cast out of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=25'>Lev 18:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=44&verse=2'>Psa 44:2</a><br/> Cast out of Canaan and their land given to Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=55'>Psa 78:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=44'>Psa 105:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=135&verse=12'>Psa 135:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=136&verse=22'>Psa 136:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=54&verse=3'>Isa 54:3</a><br/> Excluded from the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=1&verse=10'>Lam 1:10</a><br/> Wicked practices of<br/> <a href='S:Idolatry'>Idolatry</a><br/> Divine revelations given to:<br/> - Abimelech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=7'>Gen 20:7</a> <br/> - Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=28'>Gen 41:28</a> <br/> - Balaam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=22'>Num 22</a> <br/> - Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=18'>Dan 4:18</a> <br/> - Belshazzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=5'>Dan 5:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=29'>Dan 5:29</a> <br/> - Cyrus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=23'>2Ch 36:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=1&verse=4'>Ezr 1:4</a> <br/> - The magi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=11'>Mat 2:11</a> <br/> - The centurion<br/> <a href='h